public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)\\n2. 原地排序，修改原数组\\n3. 使用冒泡排序算法\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 20, \"studentAnswers\": [\"public class Solution {\\n    public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr) {\\n        if (arr == null || arr.length <= 1) {\\n            return;\\n        }\\n        int n = arr.length;\\n        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {\\n            for (int j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {\\n                if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {\\n                    int temp = arr[j];\\n                    arr[j] = arr[j + 1];\\n                    arr[j + 1] = temp;\\n                }\\n            }\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\"], \"questionContent\": \"实现冒泡排序算法，对整数数组进行升序排序。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)\\n2. 原地排序，修改原数组\\n3. 使用冒泡排序算法\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}]}','127.0.0.1','2025-11-04 09:50:18','2025-11-26 09:13:42',NULL,0,NULL,NULL),
(74,31,'{\"0\": [\"try-catch\"], \"1\": [\"override\"], \"2\": [\"extends\"], \"3\": [\"int\"], \"4\": [\"create\"], \"5\": [\"do-while\", \"for\", \"foreach\"], \"6\": [\"String\", \"StringList\", \"StringBuilder\"], \"7\": [\"IOException\", \"NullPointerException\", \"ClassNotFoundException\"], \"8\": [\"多态\", \"封装\", \"继承\"], \"9\": [\"double\", \"boolean\", \"char\"], \"10\": [\"正确\"], \"11\": [\"错误\"], \"12\": [\"错误\"], \"13\": \"SZDVXBFCN\", \"14\": \"SFDSGFDHGFH\", \"15\": \"GFDHGTJFH\", \"17\": [\"import java.util.Scanner;\\n\\npublic class Main {\\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);\\n        int n = scanner.nextInt();\\n        System.out.println(fibonacci(n));\\n        scanner.close();\\n    }\\n    \\n    public static int fibonacci(int n) {\\n        // 边界情况：F(0) = 0, F(1) = 1\\n        if (n == 0) {\\n            return 0;\\n        }\\n        if (n == 1) {\\n            return 1;\\n        }\\n        // 递归调用：F(n) = F(n-1) + F(n-2)\\n        return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2);\\n    }\\n}\\n\\n\\n\\n\"]}','{\"questions\": [{\"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"optionKey\": \"C\", \"optionContent\": \"throws\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"A\", \"optionContent\": \"try-catch\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"throw\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"D\", \"optionContent\": \"以上都是\"}], \"questionId\": 15, \"questionType\": \"SINGLE_CHOICE\", \"questionOrder\": 1, \"questionContent\": \"Java中，以下哪个是异常处理的关键字？\"}, {\"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"optionKey\": \"C\", \"optionContent\": \"extends\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"overload\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"A\", \"optionContent\": \"override\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"D\", \"optionContent\": \"不需要关键字\"}], \"questionId\": 17, \"questionType\": \"SINGLE_CHOICE\", \"questionOrder\": 2, \"questionContent\": \"Java中，以下哪个关键字用于方法重写？\"}, {\"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"implements\"}, {\"optionKey\": \"A\", \