erContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static Node reverseList(Node head) {\\n        Node prev = null;\\n        Node current = head;\\n        while (current != null) {\\n            Node next = current.next;\\n            current.next = prev;\\n            prev = current;\\n            current = next;\\n        }\\n        return prev;\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 205, \"questionText\": \"定义一个简单的链表节点类Node，然后实现反转链表的方法。\\n\\nNode类结构：\\nclass Node {\\n    int val;\\n    Node next;\\n    Node(int val) { this.val = val; }\\n}\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static Node reverseList(Node head)\\n2. 反转链表中的所有节点\\n3. 返回新的头节点\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 17, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"定义一个简单的链表节点类Node，然后实现反转链表的方法。\\n\\nNode类结构：\\nclass Node {\\n    int val;\\n    Node next;\\n    Node(int val) { this.val = val; }\\n}\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static Node reverseList(Node head)\\n2. 反转链表中的所有节点\\n3. 返回新的头节点\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 199, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static int fibonacci(int n) {\\n        if (n <= 0) {\\n            return 0;\\n        }\\n        if (n == 1) {\\n            return 1;\\n        }\\n        return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2);\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"testCases\": [{\"input\": \"0\", \"output\": \"0\"}, {\"input\": \"1\", \"output\": \"1\"}, {\"input\": \"2\", \"output\": \"1\"}, {\"input\": \"3\", \"output\": \"2\"}, {\"input\": \"5\", \"output\": \"5\"}, {\"input\": \"10\", \"output\": \"55\"}], \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 199, \"questionText\": \"编写一个Java方法，使用递归计算斐波那契数列的第n项。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static int fibonacci(int n)\\n2. 斐波那契数列定义：F(0)=0, F(1)=1, F(n)=F(n-1)+F(n-2)\\n3. 需要考虑边界情况\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 18, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"编写一个Java方法，使用递归计算斐波那契数列的第n项。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static int fibonacci(int n)\\n2. 斐波那契数列定义：F(0)=0, F(1)=1, F(n)=F(n-1)+F(n-2)\\n3. 需要考虑边界情况\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 197, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static String reverse(String str) {\\n        if (str == null || str.isEmpty()) {\\n            return str;\\n        }\\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder(str);\\n        return sb.reverse().toString();\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 197, \"questionText\": \"编写一个Java方法，实现字符串反转功能。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static String reverse(String str)\\n2. 使用StringBuilder实现\\n3. 返回反转后的字符串\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 19, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"编写一个Java方法，实现字符串反转功能。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static String reverse(String str)\\n2. 使用StringBuilder实现\\n3. 返回反转后的字符串\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 204, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Student {\\n    private String name;\\n    private int age;\\n    private double grade;\\n    \\n    public Student(String name, int age, double grade) {\\n        this.name = name;\\n        this.age = age;\\n        this.grade = grade;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public String getName() {\\n        return name;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public int getAge() {\\n        return age;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public double getGrade() {\\n        return grade;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public void setGrade(double grade) {\\n        this.grade = grade;\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 204, \"questionText\": \"创建一个Student类，包含以下属性和方法：\\n\\n属性：\\n- name (String): 学生姓名\\n- age (int): 学生年龄\\n- grade (double): 学生成绩\\n\\n方法：\\n- 构造方法：初始化所有属性\\n- getName(): 返回姓名\\n- getAge(): 返回年龄\\n- getGrade(): 返回成绩\\n- setGrade(double grade): 设置成绩\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 使用封装原则\\n2. 提供getter和setter方法\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 20, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"创建一个Student类，包含以下属性和方法：\\n\\n属性：\\n- name (String): 学生姓名\\n- age (int): 学生年龄\\n- grade (double): 学生成绩\\n\\n方法：\\n- 构造方法：初始化所有属性\\n- getName(): 返回姓名\\n- getAge(): 返回年龄\\n- getGrade(): 返回成绩\\n- setGrade(double grade): 设置成绩\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 使用封装原则\\n2. 提供getter和setter方法\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}]}','127.0.0.1','2025-11-06 09:01:50','2025-11-14 09:15:09',NULL,0,NULL,NULL),
(90,36,'{\"17\": [\"CPP:#include <iostream>\\nusing namespace std;\\n\\nint fibonacci(int n) {\\n    if (n <= 0) {\\n        return 0;\\n    }\\n    if (n == 1) {\\n        return 1;\\n    }\\n    return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2);\\n}\\n\\nint main() {\\n    int n;\\n    cin >> n;\\n    cout << fibonacci(n) << endl;\\n    return 0;\\n}\"]}','{\"questions\": [{\"id\": 15, \"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"C\", \"optionContent\": \"throws\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"A\", \"optionContent\": \"try-catch\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"throw\"}, {\"isCorrect\": true, \"optionKey\": \"D\", \"optionContent\": \"以上都是\"}], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 15, \"questionText\": \"Java中，以下哪个是异常处理的关键字？\", \"questionType\": \"SINGLE_CHOICE\", \"questionOrder\": 1, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"Java中，以下哪个是异常处理的关键字？\"}, {\"id\": 17, \"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"C\", \"optionContent\": \"extends\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"overload\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"A\", \"optionContent\": \"override\"}, {\"isCorrect\": true, \"optionKey\": \"D\", \"optionContent\": \"不需要关键字\"}], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 17, \"questionText\": \"Java中，以下哪个关键字用于方法重写？\", \"questionType\": \"SINGLE_CHOICE\", \"questionOrder\": 2, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"Java中，以下哪个关键字用于方法重写？\"}, {\"id\": 10, \"points\": 5, \"options\": [{\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"B\", \"optionContent\": \"implements\"}, {\"isCorrect\": true, \"optionKey\": \"A\", \"optionContent\": \"extends\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"C\", \"optionContent\": \"inherits\"}, {\"isCorrect\": false, \"optionKey\": \"D\", \"optionContent\": \"super\"}], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 10, \"questionText\": \"Java中