ic static int fibonacci(int n)\\n2. 斐波那契数列定义：F(0)=0, F(1)=1, F(n)=F(n-1)+F(n-2)\\n3. 需要考虑边界情况\", \"selectedLanguage\": \"CPP\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 197, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static String reverse(String str) {\\n        if (str == null || str.isEmpty()) {\\n            return str;\\n        }\\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder(str);\\n        return sb.reverse().toString();\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 197, \"questionText\": \"编写一个Java方法，实现字符串反转功能。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static String reverse(String str)\\n2. 使用StringBuilder实现\\n3. 返回反转后的字符串\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 19, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"编写一个Java方法，实现字符串反转功能。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static String reverse(String str)\\n2. 使用StringBuilder实现\\n3. 返回反转后的字符串\", \"selectedLanguage\": \"JAVA\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 204, \"points\": 5, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Student {\\n    private String name;\\n    private int age;\\n    private double grade;\\n    \\n    public Student(String name, int age, double grade) {\\n        this.name = name;\\n        this.age = age;\\n        this.grade = grade;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public String getName() {\\n        return name;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public int getAge() {\\n        return age;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public double getGrade() {\\n        return grade;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public void setGrade(double grade) {\\n        this.grade = grade;\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 204, \"questionText\": \"创建一个Student类，包含以下属性和方法：\\n\\n属性：\\n- name (String): 学生姓名\\n- age (int): 学生年龄\\n- grade (double): 学生成绩\\n\\n方法：\\n- 构造方法：初始化所有属性\\n- getName(): 返回姓名\\n- getAge(): 返回年龄\\n- getGrade(): 返回成绩\\n- setGrade(double grade): 设置成绩\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 使用封装原则\\n2. 提供getter和setter方法\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 20, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"创建一个Student类，包含以下属性和方法：\\n\\n属性：\\n- name (String): 学生姓名\\n- age (int): 学生年龄\\n- grade (double): 学生成绩\\n\\n方法：\\n- 构造方法：初始化所有属性\\n- getName(): 返回姓名\\n- getAge(): 返回年龄\\n- getGrade(): 返回成绩\\n- setGrade(double grade): 设置成绩\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 使用封装原则\\n2. 提供getter和setter方法\", \"selectedLanguage\": \"JAVA\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}]}','127.0.0.1','2025-11-06 09:18:32','2025-11-13 12:38:16',NULL,0,NULL,NULL),
