", \\\"content\\\": \\\"面向对象的三大特性是封装、继承、多态。封装是指将数据和方法包装在类中，隐藏内部实现细节；继承是指子类可以继承父类的属性和方法；多态是指同一接口可以有多种不同的实现方式。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 42, \"questionText\": \"请简述Java中面向对象的三大特性，并举例说明。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 41, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"请简述Java中面向对象的三大特性，并举例说明。\"}, {\"id\": 45, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Java集合框架以Collection接口为根，List和Set是其子接口，Map是独立的接口。List接口的实现类有ArrayList、LinkedList等；Set接口的实现类有HashSet、TreeSet等；Map接口的实现类有HashMap、TreeMap等。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 45, \"questionText\": \"请说明Java中集合框架的层次结构。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 42, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"请说明Java中集合框架的层次结构。\"}, {\"id\": 46, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Java垃圾回收机制是自动内存管理，当对象不再被任何引用变量引用时，垃圾回收器会自动回收其占用的内存。主要算法包括标记-清除算法、复制算法、标记-整理算法等，不同算法适用于不同的内存区域。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 46, \"questionText\": \"请说明Java中垃圾回收机制的基本原理。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 43, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"请说明Java中垃圾回收机制的基本原理。\"}, {\"id\": 43, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Java异常处理机制通过try-catch-finally实现。try块包含可能抛出异常的代码，catch块用于捕获和处理异常，finally块无论是否发生异常都会执行，通常用于资源清理。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 43, \"questionText\": \"请说明Java中异常处理机制，并写出try-catch-finally的基本语法。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 44, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"请说明Java中异常处理机制，并写出try-catch-finally的基本语法。\"}, {\"id\": 199, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static int fibonacci(int n) {\\n        if (n <= 0) {\\n            return 0;\\n        }\\n        if (n == 1) {\\n            return 1;\\n        }\\n        return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2);\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"testCases\": [{\"input\": \"0\", \"output\": \"0\"}, {\"input\": \"1\", \"output\": \"1\"}, {\"input\": \"2\", \"output\": \"1\"}, {\"input\": \"3\", \"output\": \"2\"}, {\"input\": \"5\", \"output\": \"5\"}, {\"input\": \"10\", \"output\": \"55\"}], \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 199, \"questionText\": \"编写一个Java方法，使用递归计算斐波那契数列的第n项。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static int fibonacci(int n)\\n2. 斐波那契数列定义：F(0)=0, F(1)=1, F(n)=F(n-1)+F(n-2)\\n3. 需要考虑边界情况\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 45, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"编写一个Java方法，使用递归计算斐波那契数列的第n项。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static int fibonacci(int n)\\n2. 斐波那契数列定义：F(0)=0, F(1)=1, F(n)=F(n-1)+F(n-2)\\n3. 需要考虑边界情况\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 205, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static Node reverseList(Node head) {\\n        Node prev = null;\\n        Node current = head;\\n        while (current != null) {\\n            Node next = current.next;\\n            current.next = prev;\\n            prev = current;\\n            current = next;\\n        }\\n        return prev;\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 205, \"questionText\": \"定义一个简单的链表节点类Node，然后实现反转链表的方法。\\n\\nNode类结构：\\nclass Node {\\n    int val;\\n    Node next;\\n    Node(int val) { this.val = val; }\\n}\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static Node reverseList(Node head)\\n2. 反转链表中的所有节点\\n3. 返回新的头节点\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 46, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"定义一个简单的链表节点类Node，然后实现反转链表的方法。\\n\\nNode类结构：\\nclass Node {\\n    int val;\\n    Node next;\\n    Node(int val) { this.val = val; }\\n}\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static Node reverseList(Node head)\\n2. 反转链表中的所有节点\\n3. 返回新的头节点\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 197, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static String reverse(String str) {\\n        if (str == null || str.isEmpty()) {\\n            return str;\\n        }\\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder(str);\\n        return sb.reverse().toString();\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 197, \"questionText\": \"编写一个Java方法，实现字符串反转功能。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static String reverse(String str)\\n2. 使用StringBuilder实现\\n3. 返回反转后的字符串\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 47, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"编写一个Java方法，实现字符串反转功能。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static String reverse(String str)\\n2. 使用StringBuilder实现\\n3. 返回反转后的字符串\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 200, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr) {\\n        if (arr == null || arr.length <= 1) {\\n            return;\\n        }\\n        int n = arr.length;\\n        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {\\n            for (int j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {\\n                if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {\\n                    int temp = arr[j];\\n                    arr[j] = arr[j + 1];\\n                    arr[j + 1] = temp;\\n                }\\n            }\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 200, \"questionText\": \"实现冒泡排序算法，对整数数组进行升序排序。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)\\n2. 原地排序，修改原数组\\n3. 使用冒泡排序算法\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 48, \"studentAnswers\": null, \"questionContent\": \"实现冒泡排序算法，对整数数组进行升序排序。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)\\n2. 原地排序，修改原数组\\n3. 使用冒泡排序算法\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}, {\"id\": 198, \"points\": 0, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"public class Solution {\\n    public static int binarySearch(int[] arr, int target) {\\n        int left = 0;\\n        int right = arr.length - 1;\\n        while (left <= right) {\\n            int mid = left + (right - left) / 2;\\n            if (arr[mid] == target) {\\n                return mid;\\n            } else if (arr[mid] < target) {\\n                left = mid + 1;\\n            } else {\\n                right = mid - 1;\\n            }\\n        }\\n        return -1;\\n    }\\n}\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": true, \"givenScore\": 0.0, \"questionId\": 198, \"questionText\": \"实现二分查找算法，在一个已排序的整数数组中查找目标值。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static int binarySearch(int[] arr, int target)\\n2. 如果找到目标值，返回其索引；否则返回-1\\n3. 数组必须是有序的\", \"questionType\": \"PROGRAMMING\", \"questionOrder\": 49, \"studentAnswers\": [\"public class Solution {\\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        // 在此处编写你的代码\\n    }\\n}的污染风险核查基本都是你妈，阿斯卡多米尼克v和别的手机啊出纳\"], \"questionContent\": \"实现二分查找算法，在一个已排序的整数数组中查找目标值。\\n\\n要求：\\n1. 方法签名：public static int binarySearch(int[] arr, int target)\\n2. 如果找到目标值，返回其索引；否则返回-1\\n3. 数组必须是有序的\", \"programmingLanguage\": \"JAVA\"}]}','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','2025-11-26 20:54:24','2025-11-26 20:55:55',NULL,0,NULL,NULL),
