ava中，String类是不可变的。\"}, {\"id\": 39, \"points\": 3, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"implements\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 39, \"questionText\": \"Java中，用于实现接口的关键字是______。\", \"questionType\": \"FILL_BLANK\", \"questionOrder\": 36, \"studentAnswers\": \"啊恶无非\", \"questionContent\": \"Java中，用于实现接口的关键字是______。\"}, {\"id\": 41, \"points\": 3, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"abstract\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 41, \"questionText\": \"Java中，用于定义抽象类的关键字是______。\", \"questionType\": \"FILL_BLANK\", \"questionOrder\": 37, \"studentAnswers\": \"实根\", \"questionContent\": \"Java中，用于定义抽象类的关键字是______。\"}, {\"id\": 45, \"points\": 2, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Java集合框架以Collection接口为根，List和Set是其子接口，Map是独立的接口。List接口的实现类有ArrayList、LinkedList等；Set接口的实现类有HashSet、TreeSet等；Map接口的实现类有HashMap、TreeMap等。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 45, \"questionText\": \"请说明Java中集合框架的层次结构。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 38, \"studentAnswers\": \"啊都不卡号不烦你擦肩\", \"questionContent\": \"请说明Java中集合框架的层次结构。\"}, {\"id\": 42, \"points\": 2, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"面向对象的三大特性是封装、继承、多态。封装是指将数据和方法包装在类中，隐藏内部实现细节；继承是指子类可以继承父类的属性和方法；多态是指同一接口可以有多种不同的实现方式。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 42, \"questionText\": \"请简述Java中面向对象的三大特性，并举例说明。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 39, \"studentAnswers\": \"水电费大V\", \"questionContent\": \"请简述Java中面向对象的三大特性，并举例说明。\"}, {\"id\": 44, \"points\": 2, \"answers\": [{\"answerContent\": \"[{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TEXT\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"String是不可变的字符串类，一旦创建就不能修改；StringBuffer是线程安全的可变字符串类，适合多线程环境；StringBuilder是非线程安全的可变字符串类，性能更好但只能在单线程环境中使用。\\\"}]\"}], \"options\": [], \"isGraded\": false, \"givenScore\": null, \"questionId\": 44, \"questionText\": \"请比较String、StringBuffer和StringBuilder的区别。\", \"questionType\": \"SUBJECTIVE\", \"questionOrder\": 40, \"studentAnswers\": \"啊单据好多个哈氏合金茶吧机\", \"questionContent\": \"请比较String、StringBuffer和StringBuilder的区别。\"}]}','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','2025-11-26 20:58:54','2025-11-26 20:59:59',NULL,0,NULL,NULL),
